  "customHelp": "(1) To Recycle a card, hold Shift while dragging the card to its deck or use the button on the Runes.\n(2) You can create Tokens and Buffs with right click on the source card.\n(3) You can mark buffed units and Damage/Might mods with 'C + click' and 'Ctrl + C + click'. You can put some status markers on cards like Buff or Temporary (center left menu).\n(4) To play a Hidden card, use Z + click on a card on your hand and then move it to the Battlefield. Then do the same to reveal it.\n(5) You can mark your points at the bottom left.\n(6) Some card will instruct you to look or reveal some cards from your Main Deck. You can do this by Right clicking the Main Deck to open the context menu and then click on Manage top cards.\n(7) Use Remove Hidden on context menu to remove unused Battlefields, otherwise it will show their names on the chat.",
